WEBVTT

00:00.021 --> 00:02.201
Previously on Genius...

00:02.202 --> 00:04.399
Picaso and I, we are the future.

00:04.400 --> 00:06.001
I wish I had a place like this.

00:06.002 --> 00:07.536
But you can work here if you want.

00:07.537 --> 00:10.538
I could give you 150
francs every month.

00:10.706 --> 00:13.275
In return, I own
everything you produce.

00:13.276 --> 00:14.509
To Picasso.

00:14.510 --> 00:16.311
To Picasso!

00:16.312 --> 00:18.079
I am in love with Germaine.

00:18.080 --> 00:19.481
I'm not in love with you.

00:19.482 --> 00:20.649
Why, why not?

00:20.650 --> 00:22.918
Because you cannot satisfy me!

00:22.919 --> 00:24.319
Carles, wait!

00:24.320 --> 00:25.587
You cannot go back to Paris.

00:25.588 --> 00:27.656
No, I'm going back to Barcelona.

00:27.657 --> 00:29.057
Carles, no, no...

00:30.526 --> 00:33.229
It's my fault. I should
never have believed him.

00:33.230 --> 00:34.497
She's his mistress?

00:34.498 --> 00:35.961
How many does he have?

00:35.962 --> 00:37.396
How many women has he painted?

00:37.397 --> 00:38.931
So you're finished with Dora?

00:38.932 --> 00:42.268
Of course not. She's brilliant.

00:42.269 --> 00:45.938
I can't remember the last time she
made me want to pick up a brush.

00:46.439 --> 00:48.574
I need something new.

00:48.608 --> 00:50.738
I want to be a painter.

00:50.739 --> 00:52.273
You will become a lawyer.

00:52.274 --> 00:54.342
Matisse is the
greatest painter in the world.

00:54.343 --> 00:56.110
But Picasso is much better-looking.

00:56.111 --> 00:58.179
We're having a
joint exhibition at a very

00:58.180 --> 00:59.914
well-respected gallery.

00:59.915 --> 01:02.669
You must come and visit me
sometime. To see some of my work.

01:02.670 --> 01:06.160
You are going to
paint her, aren't you?

